com.facebook.config

Class ConfigAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.config.ConfigAccessor

  • public class ConfigAccessor
extends Object
    1. wraps a JSONObject that contains configuration information. 2. converts JSONExceptions to a runtime ConfigException 3. provides clean conversions to primitive types and annotated bean classes
